56  [TestMethod()]
57  public void SudokuTest()
58  {
59  try
60  {
61  Handler handler = new DesktopHandler(new ClingoDesktopService(GetPath()));
62  InputProgram inputProgram = new ASPInputProgram();
63 
64  for (int i = 0; i < N; i++)
65  for (int j = 0; j < N; j++)
66  if (sudokuMatrix[i, j] != 0)
67  inputProgram.AddObjectInput(new Cell(i, j, sudokuMatrix[i, j]));
68 
69  inputProgram.AddFilesPath(".." + Path.DirectorySeparatorChar + ".." + Path.DirectorySeparatorChar + "test-resources" + Path.DirectorySeparatorChar + "asp" + Path.DirectorySeparatorChar + "sudoku");
70  handler.AddProgram(inputProgram);
71  handler.StartAsync(new CallbackAction(o =>
72  {
73  if (!(o is AnswerSets))
74  return;
75 
76  answerSets = (AnswerSets)o;
77 
78  @lock.Signal();
79  }));
80  @lock.Wait(new TimeSpan(0, 0, 0, 0, 5000));
81  Assert.IsNotNull(answerSets);
82  Assert.IsTrue(String.IsNullOrEmpty(answerSets.ErrorsString), "Found error in the Plan\n" + answerSets.ErrorsString);
83 
84  if (answerSets.Answersets.Count == 0)
85  return;
86 
87  AnswerSet @as = answerSets.Answersets[0];
88 
89  foreach (object obj in @as.Atoms)
90  {
91  Cell cell = (Cell)obj;
92  sudokuMatrix[cell.getRow(), cell.getColumn()] = cell.getValue();
93  }
94 
95  for (int i = 0; i < N; i++)
96  {
97  for (int j = 0; j < N; j++)
98  {
99  Console.Write(sudokuMatrix[i, j] + " ");
100 
101  if (sudokuMatrix[i, j] == 0)
102  Assert.Fail("NumberNotValid");
103  }
104 
105  Console.WriteLine();
106  }
107  }
108  catch (Exception e)
109  {
110  Assert.Fail("Exception " + e.Message);
111  }
112  }
113  }
